  <brief_title>Virology Follow up Study in Subjects Previously Treated With Telaprevir</brief_title>
  <official_title>EXTEND: A 3-Year, Virology Follow up Study in Subjects Previously Treated With Telaprevir in Select Clinical Studies</official_title>
